headline: Delta Electronics Enables AI-Ready Future in the Philippines at IIEE Annual National Convention and 3E XPO 2025
summary: Delta Electronics, a global leader in power and smart green solutions, will showcase its latest innovations at the 50th Institute of Integrated Electrical Engineers of the Philippines, Inc. (IIEE) Annual National Convention and 3E XPO 2025, featuring intelligent and energy-efficient technologies that support the Philippines' transition toward an AI-ready and sustainable economy. Key highlights include smart infrastructure and energy management solutions such as Delta's AI Containerized Data Cent
